                        <name type="supplied" subtype="aut">
                           <persName xml:lang="en">Naǧm al-Dīn ʾAḥmad ibn al-Minfāḫ</persName>
                           <persName xml:lang="ar">نجم الدين أحمد بن المنفاخ</persName>
                        </name>
                     </author>
                     <title xml:lang="ar-Latn-x-lc" key="work_7780">Risāla fī radd al-iʿtirāḍāt ʿalā kitāb al-Fuṣūl</title>
                     <title xml:lang="ar" key="work_7780">رسالة في رد الاعتراضات على كتاب الفصول</title>
                     <title xml:lang="en" type="desc" key="work_7780">Epistle Refuting the Objections against the Book of Aphorisms</title>
                     <note>Original manuscript in BNF.</note>
                     <note>This is a lemmatically arranged commentary (note that he only commented on a part of the lemmata). The introduction begins on f. 1b; the beginning of each Book is as follows: Bk1: 2a; Bk 2: 20a; Bk 3: 29b; (Bk 4 is lacking); Bk 5: 37b; Bk 6: 38b; Bk 7: 39b.</note>
